{"tid":13180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實LIHKG可以唔洗要中文名","createTime":"2016-11-30T02:59:15.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T23:21:28.000Z","uid":9951,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1a44c45befc3d7e32f1442dff82b7977ea314e99","tid":13180,"uid":9951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T02:59:15.000Z","msg":"你話你上開L.I.H.K.G，大佬呀五粒音，又長又難讀<br />\n見到最近好多巴絲都諗緊幫LIHKG改咩中文名好，但有冇諗過有啲野係唔一定需要中文名，例如Facebook, YouTube, Adidas咁，你叫臉書？即刻成件事柒哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以我地真正要做既，係幫&quot;LIHKG&quot;作返個英文發音<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n我個人建議不如叫Linkage，一黎即刻易讀勁多，二黎Linkage可解作聯合，代表今次各路巴絲咁齊心做低林早逝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，三黎，亦係最重要既一點<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為LIHKG呢個名係代表緊我地兩大功臣，連尼住巴打同plus仔既，所以佢唔需要亦唔應該轉串法，冇錯，我係話我地只係直接將LIHKG讀做&quot;Linkage&quot;就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n你話喂唔同串法喎，但你明白好多字既讀音，由其係名，都係約定成俗，多人啲叫叫下佢就係呢個名，反正字典又冇LIHKG既讀音，何不由我地賦與比佢？反正耳濡目染正正係我地強項<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  喂，最近&quot;Linkage&quot;又有改歌呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咦？睇唔出你都係「拎仔」喎"},{"pid":"740b2f32f792e282f65386b52845949972cf1e3c","tid":13180,"uid":9951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:11:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48f1d048cdf347e518cfdb6fdb76aeda79d37c90","tid":13180,"uid":9951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T06:23:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇人理"},{"pid":"e51d